.md
To evaluate an expression press a *play* icon or <kbd>Shift+Enter</kbd>

<details>
  <summary>List of all shortcuts:</summary>


<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:1.5rem;">

<div>

#### Cells

- <kbd>Ctrl-/</kbd>: Create fraction
- <kbd>Ctrl-6</kbd>: Power
- <kbd>Ctrl-2</kbd>: Square root
- <kbd>Ctrl--</kbd>: Subscript
- <kbd>Ctrl-=</kbd>: Semantic input
- <kbd>ESC</kbd>: Open suggestions for greek symbol
- <kbd>Alt-/</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-/</kbd>: Comment a line
- <kbd>Ctrl-F</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-F</kbd>: Search inside cell

</div>

<div>

#### Evaluation

- <kbd>Shift-Enter</kbd>: Evaluate cell
- <kbd>Ctrl-Enter</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-Enter</kbd>: Evaluate cell and jump to the next
- <kbd>Ctrl-Shift-Enter</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-Shift-Enter</kbd>: Project cell to a window
- <kbd>Alt-I</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-I</kbd>: Evaluate initialization cells

</div>

<div>

#### Notebook

- <kbd>Alt-2</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-2</kbd>: Hide/show input cell
- <kbd>Ctrl-U</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-U</kbd>: Clear output cell
- <kbd>Ctrl-N</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-N</kbd>: New notebook
- <kbd>Ctrl-S</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-S</kbd>: Save notebook
- <kbd>Ctrl-O</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-O</kbd>: Open notebook
- <kbd>Ctrl-P</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-P</kbd>: Open command palette

</div>

</div>
  
</details>

<br/><hr/>

