# Heading 1
## Heading 2

Here is a regular paragraph, which can __be styled__ in a *different way*. Then press `Shift+Enter` to make an output cell.

You can also hide an input cell automatically by a shortcut <kbd>Alt-2</kbd> or <kbd>\[CloverLeaf]-2</kbd>

$\\LaTeX$ is also supported

As well as plain HTML <span style="color:red">language</span>

